 {
  "text": "While we were wandering, we got lost.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "pc13_while_we_were_wandering_we_got_lost.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "We used to travel light on every trip.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "pc13_we_used_to_travel_light_on_every_trip.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Then I ran into an old friend at the airport.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "pc13_then_i_ran_into_an_old_friend_at_the_airport.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "It was the most eventful day of the whole trip.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "pc13_it_was_the_most_eventful_day_of_the_whole_trip.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I still have a vivid memory of that evening.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "pc13_i_still_have_a_vivid_memory_of_that_evening.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "We ended up in a village we never planned to visit.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "pc13_we_ended_up_in_a_village_we_never_planned_to_vis.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I still have a vivid memory of that day.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "pc13_i_still_have_a_vivid_memory_of_that_day.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "After a few mishaps, we ended up in a village.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "pc13_after_a_few_mishaps_we_ended_up_in_a_village.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "First, we set off early, before sunrise. While we were exploring the old town, we got completely lost. Then something unexpected happened: I ran into a long-lost friend. After a few mishaps, we ended up in a tiny village. Looking back, it was a real turning point and a vivid, unforgettable memory.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "pc13_order_story.mp3"
 }
